  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/35075fbc847fd302808cecc02d0d10ae.poster.avif?t=1727700661\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/35075fbc847fd302808cecc02d0d10ae.webm?t=1727700661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/35075fbc847fd302808cecc02d0d10ae.mp4?t=1727700661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Mini Zen Garden</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own mini zen garden in this calming sandbox game. Decorate your beautiful garden with a minimalistic set of objects. Share your garden with others, sit back, and relieve your day’s stress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌸Use 3 different tools (Build, Rotate, Remove) to express your creativity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛩️Place down cute objects to decorate your garden</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕘Gameplay time is perfect for short meditation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶An original soundtrack consisting of 2 tracks</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/284f235c7d2a4c0f9dd616a2444836af.avif?t=1727700661\" width=200 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Hi, it's SkyBrave! I make short games every month! Join my Discord channel to stay connected!</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/35075fbc847fd302808cecc02d0d10ae.poster.avif?t=1727700661\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/35075fbc847fd302808cecc02d0d10ae.webm?t=1727700661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/35075fbc847fd302808cecc02d0d10ae.mp4?t=1727700661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Mini Zen Garden</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own mini zen garden in this calming sandbox game. Decorate your beautiful garden with a minimalistic set of objects. Share your garden with others, sit back, and relieve your day’s stress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌸Use 3 different tools (Build, Rotate, Remove) to express your creativity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛩️Place down cute objects to decorate your garden</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕘Gameplay time is perfect for short meditation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶An original soundtrack consisting of 2 tracks</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826690/extras/284f235c7d2a4c0f9dd616a2444836af.avif?t=1727700661\" width=200 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Hi, it's SkyBrave! I make short games every month! Join my Discord channel to stay connected!</i></strong></p>",
